<p>The Hills District includes many suburbs with different search behaviors. A business in Pennant Hills should specify if they also serve Thornleigh, Normanhurst, and surrounding areas through their schema markup.</p>

<h3>5. Static Implementation</h3>

<p>Your business evolves – new services, changed hours, additional locations. Your schema markup should be dynamic and update automatically when you make changes to your website or business information.</p>

